**Title:** View personal information <br>
**Description:** **As a** user **I want** to view my saved name, username, age, and country on my profile page  
**So that** I can see the details I provided during registration  

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- The profile page displays the user’s name, username, age, and country  
- Information matches the data entered during registration  
- Data is read-only by default until “Edit” is selected  

**Priority:** High  
**Story Points:** 4  

